overview.en: YANT for Sanyan Community, combined with block chain and communication technology and ideas, has created a brand new "pass reading" mode, which has opened the "era of navigation" of the commercial revolution of Internet communication in China.
overview.zh: YANT来自三言社区，结合区块链和通证的技术和思想，打造出全新的“通证阅读”模式，开启了中国互联网通证商业革命的“大航海时代”。
